OL,3,C'Concerning increase' in dog attacks
OL,4,Con postal workers
OL,6,FThe number of attacks by dogs on
OL,7,Fpostal workers has increased in the
OL,8,Fpast year, with 42 incidents every
OL,9,Fweek, new research reveals.
OL,11,FRoyal Mail said there were 2,206 dog
OL,12,Fattacks in the year to March, an
OL,13,Fincrease of 15% on the previous 12
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FSome of the attacks had caused
OL,17,Fpermanent and disabling injuries to
OL,18,Fpostmen and women.
