OL,3,C'Concerning increase' in dog attacks
OL,4,Con postal workers
OL,6,FRoyal Mail launched its annual Dog
OL,7,FAwareness Week with another plea for
OL,8,Fresponsible dog ownership.
OL,10,FThe research found a concerning rise
OL,11,Fin attacks causing serious and
OL,12,Fsignificant injury to postal workers,
OL,13,Ftotalling 82 compared to 33 the
OL,14,Fprevious year.
OL,16,FHighest-risk locations were found to
OL,17,Finclude Portsmouth, Belfast , Bristol,
OL,18,FBrighton and Plymouth.
