OL,3,C'Concerning increase' in dog attacks
OL,4,Con postal workers
OL,6,F"All dog attacks can have life-
OL,7,Fchanging consequences for victims,
OL,8,Feven when the physical injury is not
OL,9,Fsignificant.
OL,11,F"Almost half of attacks happen at the
OL,12,Ffront door and over a quarter in the
OL,13,Ffront garden, so this is not just a
OL,14,FRoyal Mail issue, many other
OL,15,Forganisations face the same problem."
