OL,3,C'Concerning increase' in dog attacks
OL,4,Con postal workers
OL,6,F"The key objective of Dog Awareness
OL,7,FWeek is primarily to remind the public
OL,8,Fto be aware of their legal and moral
OL,9,Fresponsibilities to control their dogs
OL,10,Fand prevent dog attacks on postal
OL,11,Fworkers who are providing them with a
OL,12,Fgreat public service.
OL,14,F"The public need to be aware that if
OL,15,Ftheir dog attacks a postal worker,
OL,16,Fthey can be prosecuted."
